Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School infirmary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, Kanade-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like it was pretty rough even for you, Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was enough for you to serve as a leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be any Kage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing standing in the way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a guess, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the troubles that held Yuri back are fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.  Let's just use my hypnotism to find out{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by that response, it sounds like we got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Wait, that's not right at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the leader after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my problems went away that easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be the laughingstock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's use my hypnotism to{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all gone now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she admitted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade-chan, you're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just antagonistic by nature, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... that kinda makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called me Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes us seem like friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our preparations weren't wasted, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something we want to do before the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something Kanade's never done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've all moved on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because everyone helped each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not without some trouble, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.  It was only too easy for God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, one way or another...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone had a pretty good time living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's thanks to you as well, Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Takamatsu was able to move on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he'd turned into an NPC, he returned to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem all that surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say people couldn't return from being NPCs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the strength of one's feelings could one day return one's humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What song is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were humming it to yourself when we were working earlier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song that Iwasawa-san sang at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Song".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That song...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one you guys broadcast to the whole school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice song, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gymnasium?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade did the writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade-chan, you've never had a graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if it might be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like you were having fun when you were writing the letters out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls usually cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.  Girls are always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you changed for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if we'll really disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure my heart is ready for this yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you called yourself a leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that everyone's gone, you kinda lost your leader aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R...really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something's definitely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you've become more girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... should I be happy about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I be mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the fighting's over, you're an innocent and naïve little girl again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Yurippe has a cute side too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri sure is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening address!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For those who fought in the Afterlife...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinda Sekai Sensen (Afterlife Warfront) Graduation Ceremony will begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll begin by singing the War Anthem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,War Anthem?!  What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song of the SSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like a replacement for the school song.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember writing anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade also wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wrote it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, you're not even {\i1}in{\i0} the SSS!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here's the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the melody?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School songs usually tend to sound alike, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wing it.  You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with this song?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone should have checked this before we started singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kanade-chan worked hard and earnestly to write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to get so upset.  Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earnestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says right here in bold characters "feeling relaxed".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... how do I say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it's full of Kanade's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From start to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Kanade-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation Diploma Conferment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have those?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mostly Kanade again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's the principal who'll present them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I lost at Rock-Paper-Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.65,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.  The role suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always end up doing crap like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:10.76,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation Diploma Conferment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoi Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... thank you for your efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi Yuzuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata Hideki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.  Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I say?  I'm at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.  You've really helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A formal speech from the Graduating Class Representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I look back on my time here, many things have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came here, the first person I met was Nakamura Yuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She suddenly explained to me that I had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that everyone who remained in this world after death...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... were unable to accept their past lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were rebelling against God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, fought as a member of their group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After getting my memory back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to accept the life I had lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was... an irreplaceable experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted everybody else to be able to experience it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had fought back for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a very difficult thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they were all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... able to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These people gathered together in a Warfront centered around Nakamura Yuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They turned their strength into courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and began to accept their past lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,looked straight ahead and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the five of us who remain here will also graduate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I forget the faces of the comrades I've spent my time here with,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... will never forget these bonds etched into my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time we spent together was truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Representing the graduating class...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Otonashi Yuzuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing "Aogeba Toutoshi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42}TL note: This is a traditional graduation song in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious you were too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, it's your fault you were too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.98,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,We came together pretty well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really {\i1}are{\i0} different when you're with Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Closing Address!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinda Sekai Sensen Graduation Ceremonies have come to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduating students...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.  I don't want to see any women crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:12:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the one crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd never met you, Otonashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to move on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose my way any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose turn is it to cry next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I always fought against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why we weren't friends sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, as the eldest daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always had to take care of my rambunctious siblings for my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a lot of things from you, Kanade-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed so ignorant about the ways of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could've done... so much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could've done so much more, and had so much more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... this is goodbye, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really helped me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.  We'll meet somewhere again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going in order, I guess I'm next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go off and leave Kanade-chan behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, nothing would've ever started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also wouldn't have an ending like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was practically by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it, I wasn't supposed to be here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to find fulfillment in my previous life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I lost those memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ended up wandering into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I remembered all of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I was able to experience what a fulfilling life is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really were something special, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it was by accident that I ended helping everyone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's not talk forever about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see Yuri, give her my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should still have some luck left over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to use it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you like the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Very.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the end is kinda lonely, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it's like the start of a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is looking forward to starting a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe get some air...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanade...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just kinda hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.  Just like Yuri and Hinata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being sent off from a cruel life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be others who'll come here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Yuri and everyone, they might come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and suffer forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebelling against their former lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for those guys, just like this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can show them how wonderful it is to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can help them graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that I was sent here for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stay here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade, if you were to stay with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it's in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have said this before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay with you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, Kanade...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell you my feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the girl who was able to live on thanks to your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that beats in my chest, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had only one regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never able to thank the person who gave me my youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that one regret remaining in my heart, I wandered into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:19:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized it when I first stabbed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, just from that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you got the rest of your memories back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it all in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continued to hear the rhythm of your heart beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you said to me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, you'll disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you've come to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me believe them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That it is wonderful to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yuzuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, forever and ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... for loving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!
